node.text: First they stole my heart, then they stole my bed. What better way to celebrate #NationalDogDay than by signing up to join me, @BestFriendsAnimalSociety, and thousands of animal lovers for Strut Your Mutt Day on Saturday, October 23rd? You can fundraise for your favorite local participating rescue group or shelter, or if you'd like to join me on "The Gatto Pups Pack" team, I’ll be raising money for Best Friends to support their lifesaving programs across the country. The first 50 members of my team to raise $50 will get an exclusive, limited-edition team t-shirt, shown in the second photo! Click the link in my bio to join! #StrutYourMutt #SaveThemAll 📸: @mschwartzphoto

node.text: I buy my desserts by the dozen, so why not have 12 rescue dogs. Welcome to the pack Fettuccine Alfredo. This bonded brother and sister come to us via our friends at @animalhaven - rescued from the dog meat trade. Both understandably have huge trust issues, but they’re settling in quite comfortably. Last slide is before haircuts - Alfredo (the male) is on the right. @gatto_pups

node.text: To celebrate the one year anniversary of my book “The Dogfather,” I’ve added personalized thank you videos to my online store! Click the link in my bio to reserve yours now. Limited quantities available, so make sure to get yours today! Thanks for supporting me and the amazing dog rescues I have the privilege of working with.

node.text: We’re back at it, reading our daughters’ diaries on tonight’s brand new episode of #ImpracticalJokers! Don’t judge… you know you’d read it, too!

node.text: The best part about going to the aquarium with my kids is watching them try to find Nemo. I love family time and being silly with them.
